### Summary

Fixing the 5 remaining open sub-issues of the UX Overhaul epic (#296). All changes are pure frontend — no new backend endpoints needed, all required data is already in the store.

### Metadata

| Field | Value |
|-------|-------|
| Complexity | MEDIUM |
| Files to UPDATE | 4 (`BriefingPanel.tsx`, `ChatPanel.tsx`, `ThingCard.tsx`, `Sidebar.tsx`) |
